QSvgStyle
---------
* Rework animation framework
* enable caching of config values

* scrollbars: add pgup/pgdown buttons option
* lineedit : minimum width should be sufficient to show placeholder text
* add ability to animate non busy progress bars
* add ability for widgets to alter qsvgstyle theme config by using
  dynamic widget properties. e.g. qsvgstyle_frame_width=3

